WEBVTT

00:11:58.456 --> 00:12:00.032
What sort of debate is there,

00:12:00.056 --> 00:12:04.248
and what is your own view
about what your faith requires?

00:12:05.365 --> 00:12:09.984
DM: So, I chose to put on the head scarf

00:12:10.008 --> 00:12:12.828
and to wear long sleeves and long pants,

00:12:12.852 --> 00:12:16.995
and that's what I understood to be
the mainstream understanding

00:12:17.019 --> 00:12:19.707
of the requirements for covering.

00:12:20.699 --> 00:12:23.194
There is a minority opinion

00:12:23.218 --> 00:12:27.087
that says it is required for women
to also cover their face.

00:12:27.111 --> 00:12:31.360
Now, that is a legitimate opinion
within the diversity